<h2 id="section-top">Neurosurgery</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=1155">Salford Royal NHS Foundation Trust</a>
</p>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContente1293720b6224a9283c373934f1c7db5">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="patient in theatre, having surgery" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=189210"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>The Department of Neurosurgery is part of The Greater Manchester Neurosciences Centre. </p>
<p>The adult neurosurgical service is based at Salford Royal Hospital and the paediatric neurosurgical service at the Royal Manchester Children’s Hospital, Manchester. </p>
<p>For further information, <a href="http://www.srft.nhs.uk/about-us/depts/neuro-surgery/" title="visit our public site">please our section on the Salford Royal website</a>.</p>
<p> </p></div>
</div>
</div>
